<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>إِنَّهُ تعالى.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَعْلَمُ الْجَهْرَ ما يجهر به عباده.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَما يَخْفى وما يخفونه من الأقوال والأفعال.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>[سورة الأعلى <span class="c2">(٨٧)</span> : الآيات ٨ الى ٩]<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلْيُسْرى <span class="c2">(٨)</span> فَذَكِّرْ إِنْ نَفَعَتِ الذِّكْرى <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٨-<span class="c5"> وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلْيُسْرى:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَنُيَسِّرُكَ ونوفقك.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لِلْيُسْرى للطريقة البالغة اليسر فى كل أحوالك.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٩-<span class="c5"> فَذَكِّرْ إِنْ نَفَعَتِ الذِّكْرى:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَذَكِّرْ الناس.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِنْ نَفَعَتِ الذِّكْرى فشأنها أن تنفع.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>[سورة الأعلى <span class="c2">(٨٧)</span> : الآيات ١٠ الى ١٤]<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَنْ يَخْشى <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا الْأَشْقَى <span class="c2">(١١)</span> الَّذِي يَصْلَى النَّارَ الْكُبْرى <span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ثُمَّ لا يَمُوتُ فِيها وَلا يَحْيى <span class="c2">(١٣)</span> قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَنْ تَزَكَّى <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١٠-<span class="c5"> سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَنْ يَخْشى:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>سَيَذَّكَّرُ سينتفع بتذكيرك.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مَنْ يَخْشى من يخاف الله.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>١١- يَتَجَنَّبُهَا الْأَشْقَى<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>:<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يَتَجَنَّبُهَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>ويتجنب الذكرى.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>َشْقَى<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>المصر على العناد والكفر.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>١٢-<span class="c5"> الَّذِي يَصْلَى النَّارَ الْكُبْرى:</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>الَّذِي يَصْلَى الذي يدخل.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>النَّارَ الْكُبْرى المعدة للجزاء.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>١٣-<span class="c5"> ثُمَّ لا يَمُوتُ فِيها وَلا يَحْيى:</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>ثُمَّ لا يَمُوتُ فِيها فيستريح بالموت.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>وَلا يَحْيى حياة يهنأ بها.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>١٤-<span class="c5"> قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَنْ تَزَكَّى:</span><a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>قَدْ أَفْلَحَ قد فاز.<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>